org.dspace.xmlworkflow.state.actions

Interface ActionInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractXMLUIAction, AcceptEditRejectAction, ClaimAction, FinalEditAction, ReviewAction, ScoreReviewAction, SelectReviewerAction, SingleUserReviewAction

    public interface ActionInterface
    This empty interface can be implemented by the UI module(s) it does not contain any methods since each UI has there own methods of rendering the action.
